3. **Implicit Conversion Operator**: This can be a bit subtler but very powerful if used correctly. Define an operator in your `Rect` class that allows it to be implicitly converted to an `SDL_Rect`. Be cautious with this approach, as it can make the code less explicit and potentially confusing.

